at.tfr.pfad.view

Class ActivityBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.tfr.pfad.view.BaseBean
      • at.tfr.pfad.view.ActivityBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Named
 @ViewScoped
public class ActivityBean
extends BaseBean
implements Serializable
    Backing bean for Activity entities. This class provides CRUD functionality for all Activity entities. It focuses purely on Java EE 6 standards (e.g. @ConversationScoped for state management, PersistenceContext for persistence, CriteriaBuilder for searches) rather than introducing a CRUD framework or custom base class.
